Place the timer and service units in /etc/systemd/system/
Edit script and provide root directory of the syncthing folder that needs to be tracked
Ensure that script has executable rights (chmod +x)
Place the shell script in /usr/local/bin/
Reload systemd with systemctl daemon-reload
Start the timer with systemctl start syncthing-conflict-notifier.timer
Or enable it by default with systemctl enable syncthing-conflict-notifier.timer